  "description": "<p><strong>Introductions:</strong></p>\n <p>Here is our 51*51*106cm Plastic Round Birdbath with Solar Light.&nbsp; It can be used as a charming decoration to add color to your outdoor garden. It is made of high-density&nbsp; material, so it is durable. What are you waiting for, hurry up and place your order!</p>\n <p><br/></p>\n <p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n <p>1. \u3010Garden Decor for Outside --A charming decor for your outdoor garden yard with this exquisite, antique look bronzed patina bird baths of Fleur-de-Lis accents and delicate European lines</p>\n <p>2. \u3010Weather &amp; Frost Resistant Resin\u3011--The bird bath is made of lightweight high-density resin material, which is durable and holds up well through winter and summer under frost or sun exposure</p>\n <p>3. \u3010Sturdy Base\u3011--This birdbath stays in place perfectly by filling the hollow stand with sand, rocks or water to add weight to it . There are also stakes included which go into the ground unnoticeable and hold the base steady</p>\n <p>4. \u3010Easy Use\u3011Super easy to put together and celan. 25 second assembly time, no tools necessary. When it's time to clean, just dump it forward and the debris go right over the side with the old water. Really couldn't be easier</p>\n <p>5. \u3010Enjoy Watching the Birds\u3011--Place outside and enjoy a visual treat by watching a flurry of pretty birds. Birds'coming can help the soil aerate to get more water and nutrients, and protcet your garden from pests and harmful insects</p>\n <p><br/></p>\n <p><strong>Specifications:</strong></p>\n <p>1. Dimensions: (20.08 x 20.08 x 42.13)\" / (51 x 51 x 107)cm(L x W x H)</p>\n <p>2. Material: PP&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n <p>3. Weight: 5.95lbs / 2.7kg</p>\n <p>4. Color: Bronze</p>\n <p><br/></p>\n <p><strong>Package Includes:</strong></p>\n <p>1 x Birdbath</p>\n <p><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/79fc6a72-898d-4f0f-a279-72a92eb663